<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='157:183'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-1a' );" name="015-1a" class="pb">[015-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='183:191'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='191:202'>　毛詩名物解卷十五</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='202:223'>　　　　　　　　　　　宋　蔡　卞　集解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='223:228'>　雜釋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l12' data-llen='228:249'>　　　泉　　丘　　風　　憂　　賢人君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l13' data-llen='249:256'>　　　雜解</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l14' data-llen='256:261'>　　泉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l15' data-llen='261:284'>泉水之上出也故以喻政令下泉是也氿泉不正出之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l16' data-llen='284:310'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-1b' );" name="015-1b" class="pb">[015-1b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l17' data-llen='310:333'>泉而物所病也故言浸穫薪檻泉正出之泉而物所生</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l18' data-llen='333:356'>也故言采其芹秩秩斯干德澤之流有叙也豐水東注</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l19' data-llen='356:379'>順理者也滮池北流逆理者也泉源水所出而在左卑</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l20' data-llen='379:402'>也淇水泉所歸而在右尊也此尊夫卑己者也淇有岸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l21' data-llen='402:423'>岸所以自防隰有泮泮所以自辨此悔而反正也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l22' data-llen='423:428'>　　丘</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l23' data-llen='428:451'>丘者地之髙而中者也髙臣德也中臣道也黄鳥不得</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l24' data-llen='451:474'>中阿之屈以容則庶得丘隅丘側之苟可以止此大臣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l25' data-llen='474:500'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-2a' );" name="015-2a" class="pb">[015-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l26' data-llen='500:523'>遺忘微賤者楊園之道猗于畆丘楊生於卑濕㣲臣也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l27' data-llen='523:546'>畆丘大臣也以讒言之所摇常自卑以及髙邪之所歸</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l28' data-llen='546:569'>常自下以及上也旄丘前髙後下以言衞有初而無後</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l29' data-llen='569:592'>宛丘四方髙而中央下之丘也以言陳有外而無中也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l30' data-llen='592:615'>無後謂不能救亂也無中謂蕩而無守也阿丘偏髙山</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l31' data-llen='615:638'>而陟以采蝱憂傷故也丘中不平之地而猶有麻麥李</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l32' data-llen='638:651'>者言盡地以富之此思賢也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l33' data-llen='651:656'>　　風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l34' data-llen='656:682'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-2b' );" name="015-2b" class="pb">[015-2b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l35' data-llen='682:705'>凡曰風則又以爲和又以爲暴自和而言之有凱風清</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l36' data-llen='705:728'>風谷風自暴而言之有飄風終風匪風凱以言其樂之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l37' data-llen='728:751'>情清以言其微之意谷以言其和而容之道孝子慰母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l38' data-llen='751:774'>心者情也故樂長養之仁以盡其禮吉甫作頌者言也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l39' data-llen='774:797'>故歌仁言之微以動其意谷風習習和意也隂陽和則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l40' data-llen='797:820'>雨也然天之道不能常和而欲責人之常和盡人之歡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l41' data-llen='820:843'>竭人之忠此夫婦之所以道絶也故谷風有以言夫婦</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l42' data-llen='843:866'>有以言朋友終風暴而不止者也故暴而且霾霾而且</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l43' data-llen='866:892'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-3a' );" name="015-3a" class="pb">[015-3a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l44' data-llen='892:915'>曀北風威雨雪虐也所謂並爲威虐也於以動之者風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l45' data-llen='915:938'>也揭兮飄兮匪風也泉流而有迹故下泉言思治也風</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l46' data-llen='938:963'>動而無形故匪風言思道也飄風𤼵𤼵政令急也卷阿</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l47' data-llen='963:985'>亦曰飄風者君如卷阿之究則賢如飄風之疾至矣</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l48' data-llen='985:990'>　　憂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l49' data-llen='990:1013'>憂瘁病也蓋氣不舒則憯血不榮則瘁瘁者憂之見乎</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l50' data-llen='1013:1036'>色者也傳曰形容枯槁顔色憔悴蓋顔色黎黒而肌肉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l51' data-llen='1036:1059'>䵟黣則憔矣顔色柔瘠而膚革病瘦則悴矣凡此皆以</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l52' data-llen='1059:1085'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-3b' );" name="015-3b" class="pb">[015-3b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l53' data-llen='1085:1109'>憂故也夫憂之於人也聲𤼵於嘯歌液感於涕泗氣㪚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l54' data-llen='1109:1132'>於永歎形疲於假寐夏之長不能消之於晝冬之久不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l55' data-llen='1132:1155'>能消之於夜采蝱之丘而内有不能治植諼之背而外</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l56' data-llen='1155:1178'>有不能忘其苦也有至於荼其毒也有至於藥以實則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l57' data-llen='1178:1201'>爲噎以虚則爲飢以爲物所攖則如結以爲物所中則</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l58' data-llen='1201:1224'>如擣以昏則如醉又至於如酲以煩則如惔又至於如</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l59' data-llen='1224:1247'>熏其懸也如旌之摇其屬也如棋之奕其烈也如湯其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l60' data-llen='1247:1270'>慘也如隂衆焉則隱又慇獨焉則惸又至目之爲昏花</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l61' data-llen='1270:1296'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-4a' );" name="015-4a" class="pb">[015-4a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l62' data-llen='1296:1319'>也而有莪蔚之眩耳之爲聼營也而有雷霆之疑以病</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l63' data-llen='1319:1342'>其體膚也則心爲之使痗以衰其鬢髪也則身爲之用</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l64' data-llen='1342:1364'>老則憂之害人見於詩多矣豈特顔色之瘁而已哉</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l65' data-llen='1364:1372'>　　賢人君子</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l66' data-llen='1372:1395'>凡言仁人言忠臣言德言賢言君子何也柏舟言愛其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l67' data-llen='1395:1418'>君之至故所憂不能恝然忘受侮不肯翻然去此仁人</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l68' data-llen='1418:1441'>者也北門忠其君之至故窶貧摧讁之不憫從事已迫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l69' data-llen='1441:1464'>而不去以其不可如何而歸之天此忠臣者也人實迋</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l70' data-llen='1464:1490'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-4b' );" name="015-4b" class="pb">[015-4b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l71' data-llen='1490:1513'>女則忽之無忠臣者也人實不信則忽之無良士者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l72' data-llen='1513:1536'>鹿鳴有羣臣有忠臣有嘉賔何也合而言之則所宴莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l73' data-llen='1536:1559'>非臣也别而言之則示我周行者忠臣也是則是傚者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l74' data-llen='1559:1582'>嘉賔也善未至於德之充也德未至於賢之盡也兎罝</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l75' data-llen='1582:1605'>椓之丁丁而施之於中逵中林言德之隆於始也此莫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l76' data-llen='1605:1628'>不好德者也赳赳武夫公侯干城而至於好仇腹心言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l77' data-llen='1628:1651'>賢之有大於初也此賢人衆多者也簡兮之多能而言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l78' data-llen='1651:1674'>有力如虎之武執轡如組之藝執籥秉翟而不改其赫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l79' data-llen='1674:1700'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-5a' );" name="015-5a" class="pb">[015-5a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l80' data-llen='1700:1723'>如渥赭之容此所以爲賢也考槃之窮處寤言至於歌</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l81' data-llen='1723:1746'>之樂寤言至於宿之安然後憂其君而不能自己也故</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l82' data-llen='1746:1769'>永矢以絶之此所以爲賢也善人淑人以可欲言之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l83' data-llen='1769:1792'>美人淑人以充實言之也恭人以禮言哲人以智言君</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l84' data-llen='1792:1815'>子合仁智而言也君子以有德有位言也良人不爲惡</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l85' data-llen='1815:1838'>而已吉人不爲凶而已宗公所受教者也黄耇所乞言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l86' data-llen='1838:1861'>者也老成人重於典刑者也文王之聖所獨也惠於宗</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l87' data-llen='1861:1884'>公所同也宗公人謀也人謀從則鬼謀從故神㒺時怨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l88' data-llen='1884:1910'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-5b' );" name="015-5b" class="pb">[015-5b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l89' data-llen='1910:1916'>神㒺時恫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l90' data-llen='1916:1923'>　　雜解上</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l91' data-llen='1923:1946'>信足以待諸侯猶柞棫之固葉義足以制諸侯猶紼纚</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l92' data-llen='1946:1969'>之維舟韎韐士服也服士服而作六師所謂命也鞞琫</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l93' data-llen='1969:1992'>有珌諸侯之服也所謂爵也箴者箴其過戒者戒其不</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l94' data-llen='1992:2015'>及宣王銳於始而怠於終故庭燎之初箴其過以見於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l95' data-llen='2015:2038'>小雅常武之後戒其不及以見於大雅欲則易求則難</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l96' data-llen='2038:2061'>欲在意求在心欲而不求者有矣未有求而不欲者也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l97' data-llen='2061:2087'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-6a' );" name="015-6a" class="pb">[015-6a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l98' data-llen='2087:2110'>孔子曰我欲仁斯仁至矣五美以爲政欲仁者也輕國</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l99' data-llen='2110:2133'>以避地非求仁者不能也詩之辭於國之富毎言馬於</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l100' data-llen='2133:2156'>物之微每言魚蓋馬賤者也魚微者也言賤以致貴言</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l101' data-llen='2156:2179'>微以致著聖人天道之與物交者也神人天道之與物</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l102' data-llen='2179:2202'>辨者也大人人道之與物交者也至人人道之與物辨</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l103' data-llen='2202:2225'>者也親天屬也據以内恃者也賢人屬也依於内輔者</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l104' data-llen='2225:2248'>也謀欲其圖大故曰厥家戒欲其慎小故曰厥士先王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l105' data-llen='2248:2271'>使有瞽在庭者以其聼之審因其能而食焉雖食不廢</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l106' data-llen='2271:2297'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-6b' );" name="015-6b" class="pb">[015-6b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l107' data-llen='2297:2320'>也崇牙有主物之意而南方禮樂之㑹羽南方之屬文</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l108' data-llen='2320:2343'>王始造者也故其文德昭於始武王續終者也故其武</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l109' data-llen='2343:2366'>功昭於終文王倡於上武王應於下文王傳於上武王</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l110' data-llen='2366:2389'>受於下繹之而後明思之而後得酌先祖之道允師之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l111' data-llen='2389:2402'>謂矣以飬天下爾公之謂也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l112' data-llen='2402:2409'>　　雜解中</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l113' data-llen='2409:2432'>失性以天言失所以地言由之者失其道居之者失其</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l114' data-llen='2432:2455'>理喜者禮之樂樂者樂之樂藻之爲物潔蒲之爲物柔</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l115' data-llen='2455:2481'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-7a' );" name="015-7a" class="pb">[015-7a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l116' data-llen='2481:2504'>據於藻依於蒲雕如木之雕琢如鳥之啄以天命言之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l117' data-llen='2504:2527'>不可易也故太伯能譲以天性言之不可忘也故王季</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l118' data-llen='2527:2531'>能友</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l119' data-llen='2531:2538'>　　雜解下</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l120' data-llen='2538:2561'>鹿鳴之燕樂主君臣言之也皇華之忠信臣道也燕樂</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l121' data-llen='2561:2584'>以言其所交忠信以言其任四牡居二者之間所以備</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l122' data-llen='2584:2608'>君臣之道師父道也保母道也𫝊夫道也父以教之母</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l123' data-llen='2608:2631'>以生之夫以扶之裁猶裁者之裁衣範猶範者之範器</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l124' data-llen='2631:2657'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1c0011', 'WYG', '015-7b' );" name="015-7b" class="pb">[015-7b] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l125' data-llen='2657:2680'>圍猶圍者之圍所君子義以爲質仁以爲心禮以爲體</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l126' data-llen='2680:2703'>信以爲身身之者信也假之者僞也惠公之驕僖公之</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l127' data-llen='2703:2714'>願所謂無禮以體之也</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l128' data-llen='2714:2717'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l129' data-llen='2717:2720'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l130' data-llen='2720:2723'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l131' data-llen='2723:2726'>　</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l132' data-llen='2726:2737'>　毛詩名物解卷十五</span><br/>
</p>
